high_descs: turn right and walk till you're at the end of the kitchen island counter on your right, then turn right and walk to the center of that kitchen island counter and turn right to face it
grab an apple off of the kitchen island counter
turn left and walk over to the microwave in the corner of the room to your right
place the apple inside of the microwave, microwave it, then take it back out
turn left and walk forwards to the toaster on the kitchen counter on your right, stop just before the kitchen toaster
place the apple down on the kitchen counter to the right of the toaster and in front of the salt shaker
anns.task_desc: place an microwaved apple down on the kitchen counter

high_descs: Turn right and head towards the door then turn right and make your way to the counter on the right
Pick up the apple from the counter
Turn left and go around the counter to the wall, then turn left towards the microwave
Put the apple in the microwave and cook it, then remove it from the microwave
Turn left and go to the middle of the counter on the right
Put the apple on the counter in front of the salt shaker
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved apple on the counter

high_descs: Turn right and walk around the kitchen island.
Continue around the kitchen island to the microwave on the left.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Place the apple on the counter in front of the salt shaker.
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple on a counter.
